        <mxCell id="rmNote" value="파이프라인: admission → retrieval/context → 세션 배칭&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#8A5A08&quot;&gt;retrieval chunk 목록 → Router의 KV 재사용 판정 입력&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#6B7A90;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
